solus-installer

        About
                solus-installer is an installer for the Solus operating system.

	Dependencies
		* binutils
		* gtk-3-dev
		* libparted-dev
		* pkg-config

        Compiling
                Navigate to the root directory of solus-installer and run the following command:
                        sh install.sh
        
        Running
                After compiling solus-installer, enter the following command:
                        ./solus-installer
        
